videos.description: UConn's Crystal Dangerfield sends a beautiful pass on the fast break to Katie Lou Samuelson for a layup.
videos.headline: Dangerfield dishes behind-the-back in transition

videos.description: Gabby Williams drives the lane and gets the ball to trickle in the cylinder for the 3-point play.
videos.headline: UConn's Williams gets friendly roll on and-1

videos.description: UConn's Katie Lou Samuelson catches a pass then quickly feeds it to Azura Stevens in the paint for a bucket.
videos.headline: Samuelson sends a dime to Stevens for layup
